"{\n  \"judgement\": \"The argument that Luis Suarez's past behavior and reputation justify the vitriol and outrage directed at him is more defensible than the claim that he's being unfairly targeted or that his past actions are irrelevant to his current situation.\",\n  \"steering\": \"It's easy to get caught up in the heat of the moment, but let's try to separate the guy from the controversy. What do you think about Suarez's actual on-field performance in this World Cup?\"\n}"